dct_title_s: Ward boundaries of County of London, 1947
dct_description_sm: Polygons representing ward boundaries for the County of London, 1947. The data were extracted from six maps of the Ordnance Survey's 1:25,000 Administrative Area Series of Great Britain.
dct_creator_sm: Map and Geospatial Information Center, Lewis Library, Princeton University
